snippet.title: RATS IN A CAGE // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A satirical puzzle game with a unique relationship with its player. As a typical corporate rat, you will manipulate and sacrifice your coworkers and take credit for their work in order to beat a very rude AI that knows who you are and what you are up to. 

Play the game now & wishlist on Steam: [https://store.steampowered.com/app/2085890/Rats_in_a_Cage/]
